Type: Planète tellurique
Paysage: Sols arides et rocheux, orages cosmiques
Especes: —
Description: BopMalastare
Planet located in the galaxy's"Unknown Regions", considered to be the homeworld of the Sith. The planet served the lair of Emperor Palpatine after his defeat and apparent death at Endor. It was also the site of a massive battle between Final Order forces and the Resistance and its allies, which marked the end of the conflict between Resistance and the First Order, as well as the Sith, with the death of Palpatine.
L'ordre Sith y est partiellement issu.
